{"metadata":{"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"FlyHUD"}],"title":"Overview"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"SDK Positioning","anchor":"SDK-Positioning"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"FlyHUD is a lightweight, high-performance HUD (Heads-Up Display) library for Apple platforms."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It serves as a drop-in solution for displaying transient status information — such as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"loading spinners, progress bars, success\/error indicators, and toast messages — without"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"blocking the user interface or requiring complex view controller orchestration."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Core Design Principles","anchor":"Core-Design-Principles"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Minimal footprint"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — No external dependencies; pure UIKit"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Thread-safe API"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — All public methods are "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"type":"text","text":"-isolated"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Composable"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Mix and match indicator, progress, and custom views"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Customizable"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Fine-grained control over layout, animation, and appearance"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accessible"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Full VoiceOver support (modal focus, escape gesture, dynamic labels, contextual hints, progress announcements), Dynamic Type, and RTL layouts"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Architecture","anchor":"Architecture"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"FlyHUD follows a modular architecture with clear dependency boundaries:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"architecture.svg"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"text","type":"codeListing","code":["┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐","│                  Your App                        │","├────────────────┬────────────────┬───────────────┤","│ FlyIndicatorHUD│  FlyProgressHUD│ FlyHUDSwiftUI │","├────────────────┴────────────────┴───────────────┤","│                    FlyHUD                        │","│  ┌──────────┐ ┌───────────┐ ┌────────────────┐ │","│  │   HUD    │ │ContentView│ │ BackgroundView │ │","│  │ (root)   │ │(indicator,│ │ (blur, solid,  │ │","│  │          │ │ labels,   │ │  glass)        │ │","│  │          │ │ button)   │ │                │ │","│  └──────────┘ └───────────┘ └────────────────┘ │","│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐   │","│  │  Observables: DisplayLink, Keyboard      │   │","│  └──────────────────────────────────────────┘   │","├─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤","│                    UIKit                         │","└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘"]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Module Responsibilities","anchor":"Module-Responsibilities"},{"type":"table","header":"row","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Module"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Target"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Responsibility"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"FlyHUD"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FlyHUD"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Core HUD container, layout engine, animation system, background styles, keyboard tracking"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"FlyHUDSwiftUI"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FlyHUDSwiftUI"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI declarative modifiers, UIKit bridge, convenience presets"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"FlyIndicatorHUD"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FlyIndicatorHUD"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Custom activity indicator animations (ring, ball spin, circle stroke, arc dot)"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"FlyProgressHUD"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FlyProgressHUD"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Custom progress view styles (bar, round, annular, pie)"}]}]]]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Dependency Direction","anchor":"Dependency-Direction"},{"syntax":"text","type":"codeListing","code":["FlyIndicatorHUD ──depends on──▶ FlyHUD ◀──depends on── FlyProgressHUD","                                  ▲","                                  │","                            FlyHUDSwiftUI"]},{"style":"important","name":"Important","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FlyHUD"},{"type":"text","text":" must never import "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FlyIndicatorHUD"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FlyProgressHUD"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FlyHUDSwiftUI"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Reverse dependencies are strictly forbidden."}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"View Hierarchy","anchor":"View-Hierarchy"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When displa